node.text:
Just in case you missed it, here’s a quick recap from the Steve Harvey Invitational Golf Classic presented by @lexususa. Thank you Lexus for being our presenting sponsor and champion for the life work that The @harvey.foundation has committed to. 

With your support we are able to change the lives of disadvantaged youth by cultivating the next generation of responsible leaders and providing educational enrichment, mentoring, life transformation skills, and global service initiatives. 

Thank you to all of our participants and sponsors for your continued support!

Thank you to all of our participants and sponsors for your continued support!
